BookNest: A Hotel Management System
Functional Requirements
 
1. User Management
1.1 Manager (Administrator)
•	Full access to the system
•	Manage employee accounts
•	Assign user roles and permissions
•	View all bookings and guest records
•	Manage room information
•	Approve discounts and refunds
•	Manage salaries
•	View reports and analytics
•	Manage hotel services
•	System settings
1.2 Receptionist
•	Register guests
•	Manage bookings
•	Check room availability
•	Check-in guests
•	Check-out guests
•	Collect payments
•	Generate invoices
•	Update guest information
•	Create service requests
•	View booking history
1.3 Housekeeping Staff
•	Attendance through attendance machine
•	View assigned rooms
•	Update cleaning status
•	Report damaged items
•	Report maintenance issues
1.4 Maintenance Staff
•	View maintenance requests
•	Update maintenance status
•	Mark maintenance as completed
•	Report repair costs
 
